==Introduction==
The Wiki Automation Tool provides a generic mechanism to '''map properties from one Concept to the properties of another Concept''' (to state that they are represent the same thing).

In most cases this mechanism is used to map specific Concepts defined in the Data Model to well-known Concepts implemented in the Wiki Automation Tool.
Wiki Automation Tool provides several widgets which are based on well-known Concept (e.g. Task).
Mapping specific Concepts from the Model to these Concepts allows to provide these generic widgets also for specific Concepts.

This feature is used to implement the following widgets:
* [[Help:Gantt Chart|Gantt Chart]]


==Definition==
<pre>
<concept name="{TARGET CONCEPT}">                      <!-- might be well-known Concept -->
  <structure>
    <property name="{TARGET CONCEPT PROPERTY}"/>
  </structure>
</concept>

<concept name="{SOURCE CONCEPT}">
  <structure>
    <property name="{SOURCE CONCEPT PROPERTY}"/>
  </structure>

  <conceptMapping name="{TARGET CONCEPT}" function="{MAPPING FUNCTION}">
    <propertyMapping name="{TARGET CONCEPT PROPERTY}" property="{SOURCE CONCEPT PROPERTY}" refersTo="{REFERRED CONCEPT}" value="{STATIC VALUE}"/>
    ...
    <subobjectMapping name="{TARGET SUBOBJECT PROPERTY}" subobject="{SOURCE SUBOBJECT PROPERTY}">
      <propertyMapping name="{TARGET CONCEPT PROPERTY}" property="{SOURCE CONCEPT PROPERTY}" refersTo="{REFERRED CONCEPT}" value="{STATIC VALUE}"/>
      ..
    </subobjectMapping>
  </conceptMapping>

</concept>
</pre>

{| class="helptable"
|-
! {SOURCE CONCEPT}
| A short name of the Source Concept, which is mapped to the Target Concept.
|-
! {SOURCE CONCEPT PROPERTY}
| A name of the Property in the Source Concept, which is mapped to one of the Properties in the Target Concept.
|-
! {TARGET CONCEPT}
| A short name of the Target Concept, into which the Source Concept is mapped to.
|-
! {MAPPING FUNCTION}
| A purpose of this mapping. The following options are allowed:
* DeriveData
* GanttChart
Depending on this value WAT generates required pages.
|-
! {TARGET CONCEPT PROPERTY}
| A name of the Property in the Target Concept, into which the Property from the Source Concept is mapped to.
|-
! {TARGET SUBOBJECT PROPERTY}
| A name of the Subobject property in the Target Concept
|-
! {SOURCE SUBOBJECT PROPERTY}
| A name of the Subobject property in the Source Concept
|-
! {STATIC VALUE}
| A static value assigned to the Property in the Target Concept.
|}


==Semantic database==
Not applicable.


==Example==
<pre>
<concept name="Project" >
  <structure>
    <property name="Title"/>
    <property name="Description"/>
    <property name="Start date"/>
    <property name="End date"/>
  </structure>

  <conceptMapping name="team::Task" function="GanttChart">
    <propertyMapping name="Label" property="Title"/>
    <propertyMapping name="Start" property="Start date"/>
    <propertyMapping name="End" property="End date"/>
    <propertyMapping name="Resource" value="Technology and Human Factors Branch"/>
    <propertyMapping name="Unit" value="quarter"/>
    <propertyMapping name="Open Levels" value="3"/>
    <propertyMapping name="Notes" property="Description"/>
    <propertyMapping name="Caption" value="Resource"/>
  </conceptMapping>
</concept>


<conceptMapping name="Test Case" function="DeriveData">
  <propertyMapping name="Is tested during" value="CWIX 2018"/>
  <propertyMapping name="Is derived from" value="{{PAGENAME}}"/>
  <propertyMapping name="Test case status" value="Initial Draft"/>
  <propertyMapping name="Keyword" property="Keyword"/>
  <propertyMapping name="Is testing" property="Is testing" refersTo="Standard"/>
  <propertyMapping name="Is testing" property="Is testing" refersTo="Service"/>
  <propertyMapping name="Is testing" property="Is testing" refersTo="Information Product"/>
  <propertyMapping name="Protocol" property="Protocol"/>
  <propertyMapping name="Description" property="Description"/>
  <propertyMapping name="Precondition" property="Precondition"/>
  <propertyMapping name="Validation criteria" property="Validation criteria"/>
  <subobjectMapping name="Step object" subobject="Step object">
    <propertyMapping name="Order" property="Order"/>
    <propertyMapping name="Description" property="Description"/>
    <propertyMapping name="Expected result" property="Expected result"/>
  </subobjectMapping>
</conceptMapping>

</pre>

In the example above the "Project" Concept is mapped to well-known Concept in Wiki Automation Tool: '''"team::Task"'''


==User Interface==
The mapping information is used to configure various widgets which are based on the well-known Concepts.
